    shabd:belongsTo sggs:ang555_shabd17 ;
    shabd:gurmukhi "ਆਪਣਿਆ ਸੇਵਕਾ ਕੀ ਆਪਿ ਪੈਜ ਰਖੈ ਆਪਣਿਆ ਭਗਤਾ ਕੀ ਪੈਰੀ ਪਾਵੈ ॥"@pa ;
    shabd:transliteration "Āpaṇiā sevakā kī āp paij rakhai, āpaṇiā bhagtā kī pairī pāvai."@en-Latn ;
    shabd:translationEn "He Himself preserves the honor of His servants; He Himself bows at the feet of His devotees."@en ;
    shabd:hasTheme shabd:DivineProtection,
                   shabd:DivineHumility,
                   shabd:Bhagat ;
    shabd:commentaryKeypoint "God personally safeguards the honor of His servants and exalts His devotees with such love that He is poetically described as bowing at their feet, revealing Divine humility."@en ;
