    shabd:hasTheme shabd:UniversalLove,
                   shabd:Restlessness ;
    shabd:commentaryKeypoint "The one loved by the Divine naturally becomes beloved of all beings, radiating universal love, while those without this Divine connection remain in cycles of restless wandering and coming and going."@en ;
